    <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
<p>Donated by Richard Hull in 2015. The accession number associated with this gift is 2016.008.</p>  </acqinfo>
  <processinfo id="aspace_2738ff76431a21519da19ed29e122ae0">
